riginal_name":"Sithembiso Sontshaka","popularity":0.4832,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5e9b28c64a4bfc001cd4eb09","department":"Crew","job":"Special Effects Technician"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2144255,"known_for_department":"Crew","name":"Emil Snyman","original_name":"Emil Snyman","popularity":0.3088,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5e9b28af076ce800242ccb80","department":"Crew","job":"Special Effects Technician"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2144245,"known_for_department":"Crew","name":"Mxolisi Alfred Mkhutshwa","original_name":"Mxolisi Alfred Mkhutshwa","popularity":0.2681,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"5e9b2896eb79c200205b939d","department":"Crew","job":"Special Effects Technician"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1896841,"known_for_department":"Art","name":"James Nilsen-Misra","original_name":"James Nilsen-Misra","popularity":0.0637,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"6899b5636c45426dd35d147d","department":"Art","job":"Set Dresser"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2716118,"known_for_department":"Art","name":"Karl du Preez","original_name":"Karl du Preez","popularity":0.0498,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"6899b58eb4a132ba0d8dac6a","department":"Art","job":"Leadman"},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2374089,"known_for_department":"Crew","name":"Sam Willoughby","original_name":"Sam Willoughby","popularity":0.4244,"profile_path":"/57iNn6AS2qw6HGFAkch85WPvIJK.jpg","credit_id":"698a13aca5a58baa5d2cf273","department":"Crew","job":"Stunts"}]}},"person_24422_translations":{"at":1774727003367,"data":{"id":24422,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Bernard Fresson (27 May 1931- 20 October 2002) was a French cinema actor. He starred in over 160 films. Some of his notable roles include: Javert in the 1972 mini-series version of Les Misérables, Inspector Barthelmy in John Frankenheimer's French Connection II (1974), Scope in Roman Polanski's The Tenant (1976), Gilbert in Lover Boy (1978), and Francis in Garçon! (1983), for which he received a César nomination for Best Supporting Actor.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Bernard Fresson, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.​","name":"Bernard Fresson","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Bernard René Pierre Fresson est né à Reims le 27/05/1931. Après le lycée privé Sainte-Geneviève et HEC — promotion Europe —, dont il sort major, il entre à l'école d'art dramatique Tania Balachova. Il travaille tout d'abord avec Jean Vilar. Avec des metteurs en scène comme Roger Planchon ou Robert Hossein, il joue William Shakespeare, Roland Dubillard en passant par Paul Claudel et Peter Ustinov… Alain Resnais le fait débuter au cinéma à 28 ans, en 1959, avec un petit rôle de soldat allemand dans Hiroshima mon amour. Mais c'est réellement à la fin des années 1960, avec ce même réalisateur, qu'il se distinguera notamment dans Je t'aime, je t'aime ou La guerre est finie. Il jouera pour Jean Renoir, Henri-Georges Clouzot, Roman Polanski, Philippe Labro, Costa-Gavras, Claude Sautet, Nicole Garcia, Christophe Gans, Yves Boisset et Joël Séria. On le verra avec Philippe Léotard, dans la distribution française de la super-production hollywoodienne French Connection 2, de John Frankenheimer, aux côtés de Gene Hackman, où il joue en anglais.\n\nBernard Fresson est nommé à deux reprises aux César, pour Garçon ! en 1984, et pour Place Vendôme en 1999\n\nPour la télévision, il a tourné dans Les Compagnons de Jéhu de Michel Drach, en 1965, dans Les Cinq Dernières Minutes, en 1967, et dans Jean Jaurès, vie et mort d'un socialiste d'Ange Casta, en 1979. En 1974, il est en tête d'affiche de la série Jo Gaillard, première série tournée en couleurs pour la 1re chaîne\n\nAprès le général Delestraint, dans Jean Moulin, une affaire française aux côtés de Francis Huster, il fera sa dernière apparition dans La bataille d'Hernani où il incarne Victor Hugo.\n\nHommage à B. Fresson, cimetière de l'est à Reims\n\nIl a doublé en français le sergent Hartman dans Full Metal Jacket de Stanley Kubrick.\n\nMort d'un cancer le 20 octobre 2002 à 71 ans, il a été incinéré au cimetière du Père-Lachaise à Paris.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bernard Fresson","primary":true}}]}},"person_61160_translations":{"at":1774727004354,"data":{"id":61160,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Marina Stephenson Kerr (born September 26, 1962) is a Canadian actress with fourty years experience on screen and stage. Her work encompasses many genres including musical, comedy, drama, horror, and MOW.","name":"Marina Stephenson Kerr","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玛丽娜·斯蒂芬森·可儿（Marina Stephenson Kerr）是加拿大女演员。","name":"玛丽娜·斯蒂芬森·可儿","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"瑪麗娜·斯蒂芬森·可兒（Marina Stephenson Kerr）是加拿大女演員。","name":"瑪麗娜·斯蒂芬森·可兒","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Марина Стивенсон Керр","primary":false}}]}},"person_141701_translations":{"at":1774727006058,"data":{"id":141701,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ramya Krishnan is an Indian film actress. She has acted in over 200 films in five languages: Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam and Hindi.","name":"Ramya Krishnan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"te","name":"తెలుగు","english_name":"Telugu","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ramya Krishnan","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"拉米亚·克里希南（Ramya Krishnan）是印度电影女演员。她用五种语言出演了 200 多部电影：泰米尔语、泰卢固语、卡纳达语、马拉雅拉姆语和印地语。她主要出演了近 100 部泰卢固语电影和 60 部泰米尔语电影。","name":"拉米亚·克里希南","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AE","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"راميا كريشنان","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"راميا كريشنان","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"拉米亞·克裏希南（拉姆亞·克李希南）是印度電影女演員。她用五種語言出演了 200 多部電影：泰米爾語、泰盧固語、卡納達語、馬拉雅拉姆語和印地語。她主要出演了近 100 部泰盧固語電影和 60 部泰米爾語電影。","name":"拉姆亞·克李希南","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拉姆亞·克李希南","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SG","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"拉米亚·克里希南（Ramya Krishnan）是印度电影女演员。她用五种语言出演了 200 多部电影：泰米尔语、泰卢固语、卡纳达语、马拉雅拉姆语和印地语。她主要出演了近 100 部泰卢固语电影和 60 部泰米尔语电影。","name":"拉姆亚·克里希南","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"รามยา กริชนาน","primary":false}}]}},"person_1948606_translations":{"at":1774727012415,"data":{"id":1948606,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"May Hong (born October 24, 1988) is an American model, actress, and artist. She has most notably modeled for designers including Eckhaus Latta, Marc Jacobs, and Gucci. As an actress, Hong has appeared on High Maintenance, Hacks, Tales of the City, and the animated film KPop Demon Hunters.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article May Hong, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"May Hong","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"메이 홍","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мэй Хонг","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"May Hong ist eine amerikanische Schauspielerin, Model und Künstlerin koreanischer Herkunft, geboren etwa 1988 in Südkorea und im Alter von sechs Jahren in die USA eingewandert. Sie wuchs in Flushing, Queens, New York, auf und besuchte die Fiorello LaGuardia High School, wo sie Kunst studierte. Anschließend absolvierte sie ein Bachelorstudium in Printmaking an der Rhode Island School of Design (RISD).\n\nIhre Karriere begann als Model, unter anderem für Designer wie Eckhaus Latta, Marc Jacobs, Gucci, Adidas, Marni und Telfar. Sie lief regelmäßig bei New York Fashion Week und ist ein Stammmodel bei Eckhaus Latta.\n\nAls Schauspielerin ist May Hong bekannt für Rollen in TV-Serien wie Tales of the City (2019, als Margot Park), High Maintenance, Hacks, New Amsterdam und Up Here. Außerdem wirkte sie in Filmen wie Adam (2019) mit und lieh 2025 der Figur Mira in dem animierten Film KPop Demon Hunters ihre Stimme.\n\nSie lebt in Brooklyn, New York, und identifiziert sich als queer.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"梅·洪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"梅·洪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мей Хон","primary":false}}]}},"person_1238642_translations":{"at":1774727019687,"data":{"id":1238642,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kim Jeong-hoon (김정훈) is a South Korean actor and former singer as a member of the duo UN.  He is known in Japan under the name John Hoon.","name":"Kim Jeong-hoon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韩国歌手、男演员。曾就读于韩国首尔大学牙医预科，因追求演艺事业，于2003年选择退学，后进入中央大学戏剧学院。2000年金桢勋和崔正元以男子组合UN的形式出道，2005年组合解散。后因在人气电视剧《宫》中饰演男二号“律王子”一角，红遍全亚洲。2009年4月28日入伍服兵役，服役期间表现优异，获得军队授予模范士兵，2011年2月28日金桢勋退役。","name":"金桢勋","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"김정훈","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國歌手、男演員。曾就讀於韓國首爾大學牙醫預科，因追求演藝事業，於 2003 年選擇退學，後進入中央大學戲劇學院。2000 年金楨勳和崔正元以男子組合 UN 的形式出道，2005 年組合解散。後因在人氣電視劇《宮》中飾演男二號“律王子”一角，紅遍全亞洲。2009 年 4 月 28 日入伍服兵役，服役期間表現優異，獲得軍隊授豫模範士兵，2011 年 2 月 28 日金楨勳退役。","name":"金楨勳","primary":false}}]}}}}